---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Agenda una demo — Sacs"
  description="Agenda una demo de 30 minutos. Cargamos tus productos y datos reales en Sacs para que veas punto de venta, inventario, CRM y reportes funcionando con tu negocio."
>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="ct-hero">
  <div class="ct-hero-inner">
    <div class="ct-hero-text">
      <h1 class="ct-h1">Conoce Sacs<br/>en 30 minutos</h1>
      <p class="ct-lead">Cargamos tus productos, tu inventario y tus datos reales en Sacs para que veas exactamente como funciona con tu negocio. Sin presentaciones, sin presion.</p>
      <div class="ct-session">
        <p class="ct-session-label">En la sesion:</p>
        <div class="ct-session-steps">
          <div class="ct-session-step">
            <span class="ct-session-num">1</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Entendemos tu operacion</strong>
              <p>Cuantas tiendas tienes, como vendes hoy, que quieres controlar mejor: ventas, inventario, clientes o todo junto.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-session-step">
            <span class="ct-session-num">2</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Abrimos Sacs con tus datos</strong>
              <p>Punto de venta, control de inventario multi-sucursal, CRM de clientes, reportes — lo configuramos en vivo para tu giro.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-session-step">
            <span class="ct-session-num">3</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Definimos tu plan de arranque</strong>
              <p>Migracion de datos, capacitacion de equipo y tiempos de implementacion. Sales con un plan concreto.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Inline stats -->
      <div class="ct-hero-stats">
        <div class="ct-hero-stat">
          <span class="ct-stat-num">3,000+</span>
          <span class="ct-stat-label">marcas activas</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ct-stat-sep"></div>
        <div class="ct-hero-stat">
          <span class="ct-stat-num">4.8/5</span>
          <span class="ct-stat-label">en Google</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ct-stat-sep"></div>
        <div class="ct-hero-stat">
          <span class="ct-stat-num">99.9%</span>
          <span class="ct-stat-label">uptime</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quote -->
      <blockquote class="ct-hero-quote">
        <p>"La plataforma nos dio el control que necesitabamos para escalar a 42 sucursales."</p>
        <cite>— La Bella Pandita</cite>
      </blockquote>

      <!-- Trusted -->
      <div class="ct-hero-trusted">
        <span class="ct-trusted-label">Confian en Sacs</span>
        <div class="ct-trusted-names">
          <span>La Bella Pandita</span>
          <span>Liveshow</span>
          <span>Casa Maca</span>
          <span>Sandmade</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ct-hero-cal" id="demo">
      <div class="calendly-inline-widget" data-url="https://calendly.com/aaronherzberg/reuniongeneral?hide_event_type_details=1&hide_gdpr_banner=1" style="min-width:320px;height:700px;"></div>
      <script type="text/javascript" src="https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js" async></script>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Social proof strip -->
<section class="ct-proof">
  <div class="ct-proof-inner">
    <div class="ct-proof-item">
      <span class="ct-proof-num">3,000+</span>
      <span class="ct-proof-label">marcas activas</span>
    </div>
    <span class="ct-proof-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <div class="ct-proof-item">
      <span class="ct-proof-num">4.8/5</span>
      <span class="ct-proof-label">Google Reviews</span>
    </div>
    <span class="ct-proof-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <div class="ct-proof-item">
      <span class="ct-proof-num">99.9%</span>
      <span class="ct-proof-label">uptime</span>
    </div>
    <span class="ct-proof-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <div class="ct-proof-item">
      <span class="ct-proof-num">15 min</span>
      <span class="ct-proof-label">para configurar</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Process -->
<section class="ct-process">
  <div class="ct-process-inner">
    <p class="ct-eyebrow">Como funciona</p>
    <h2 class="ct-h2">Que esperar de la reunion</h2>
    <div class="ct-process-grid">
      <div class="ct-process-card">
        <span class="ct-process-num">1</span>
        <h3>Entendemos tu operacion</h3>
        <p>Cuantas tiendas manejas, como controlas inventario, como cobras, que informacion te falta para tomar decisiones.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-process-card">
        <span class="ct-process-num">2</span>
        <h3>Demo con tus datos reales</h3>
        <p>Cargamos tus productos y configuramos Sacs para tu giro: punto de venta, inventario multi-sucursal, CRM, reportes y facturacion.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-process-card">
        <span class="ct-process-num">3</span>
        <h3>Plan de arranque concreto</h3>
        <p>Sales con fechas de migracion, capacitacion de equipo y todo lo que necesitas para operar con Sacs en dias, no meses.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- After the demo -->
<section class="ct-after">
  <div class="ct-after-inner">
    <p class="ct-eyebrow">Despues de la demo</p>
    <h2 class="ct-h2">De la reunion a operar en 24 horas</h2>
    <div class="ct-after-grid">
      <div class="ct-after-card">
        <div class="ct-after-badge">En la llamada</div>
        <h3>Propuesta a tu medida</h3>
        <p>Te presentamos un plan personalizado basado en tu tamano y necesidades. Transparente, sin letras chiquitas.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-after-card ct-after-card--accent">
        <div class="ct-after-badge ct-after-badge--accent">Mismo dia</div>
        <h3>Cuenta activa</h3>
        <p>Si aceptas, tu cuenta se habilita ese mismo dia. Sin esperas, sin procesos largos.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-after-card">
        <div class="ct-after-badge">Dia siguiente</div>
        <h3>Asesoria de inicio</h3>
        <p>Un experto te acompana para configurar catalogo, inventario y punto de venta. Al dia siguiente ya operas.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Migration + No risk -->
<section class="ct-migrate">
  <div class="ct-migrate-inner">
    <div class="ct-migrate-left">
      <p class="ct-eyebrow">Si decides iniciar</p>
      <h2 class="ct-h2" style="margin-bottom:var(--space-5)">Migrar es mas facil de lo que piensas</h2>
      <p class="ct-migrate-desc">Nuestro equipo migra tu catalogo, clientes e historial de ventas. Tu solo validas. Sin perder un dia de ventas.</p>
      <div class="ct-migrate-steps">
        <div class="ct-migrate-step">
          <span class="ct-migrate-num">1</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Nos envias tu catalogo</strong>
            <p>Excel, CSV o desde tu sistema actual. Nosotros lo formateamos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ct-migrate-step">
          <span class="ct-migrate-num">2</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Importamos todo en 1-3 dias</strong>
            <p>Productos, variantes, precios, clientes y proveedores.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ct-migrate-step">
          <span class="ct-migrate-num">3</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Vendes desde el dia 1</strong>
            <p>Capacitacion incluida. Tu ejecutivo te acompana en cada paso.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ct-migrate-right">
      <div class="ct-norisk-card">
        <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="var(--color-secondary)" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M8 12l3 3 5-5" stroke="var(--color-secondary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        <h3>Sin riesgo</h3>
        <p>Prueba 7 dias gratis. Sin tarjeta. Si no te convence, cancelas con un clic. Sin llamadas, sin retencion, sin letra chiquita.</p>
        <p class="ct-norisk-extras">Migracion incluida &middot; Soporte 24/7 &middot; Cancela cuando quieras</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ct-bonus-card">
        <h3>Consultoria de implementacion gratis</h3>
        <p>Normalmente tiene un costo de <strong>$8,000 MXN</strong>. Con tu plan anual, la consultoria personalizada de implementacion es completamente gratis. Un experto disena contigo la estrategia para que saques el maximo de Sacs desde el dia uno.</p>
        <span class="ct-bonus-badge">Incluido con plan anual</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Testimonial -->
<section class="ct-quote-section">
  <div class="ct-quote-inner">
    <blockquote class="ct-blockquote">
      <p>"En un concierto llegamos a perder el 20% de nuestras ventas en solo dos horas porque el sistema cayo. Con Sacs eso no vuelve a pasar."</p>
      <footer>
        <cite>Mariana Lopez</cite>
        <span>Directora de Operaciones, Liveshow Merchandising</span>
      </footer>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WhatsApp alternative -->
<section class="ct-wa">
  <div class="ct-wa-inner">
    <p class="ct-wa-text">Prefieres chatear? Escribenos directo por WhatsApp.</p>
    <a id="demo-wa-link" href="https://wa.me/5215536634392" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ct-wa-btn">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
      Escribenos por WhatsApp
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════
     Contacto — Refined Squarespace style
     ═══════════════════════════════════════ */

  /* ── Shared ── */
  .ct-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
  }
  .ct-h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.625rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-10);
  }

  /* ── Hero ── */
  .ct-hero {
    background: #fff;
    padding: clamp(100px, 10vw, 140px) 0 clamp(64px, 8vw, 96px);
  }
  .ct-hero-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(24px, 4vw, 48px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.15fr;
    gap: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .ct-h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5);
  }
  .ct-lead {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.4vw, 1.1rem);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-8);
    max-width: 440px;
  }
  .ct-session {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  .ct-session-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-3);
  }
  .ct-session-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .ct-session-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .ct-session-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--color-primary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .ct-session-step strong {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    display: block;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .ct-session-step p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.45;
    margin: 2px 0 0;
  }

  /* Hero stats */
  .ct-hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }
  .ct-stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .ct-stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    display: block;
    margin-top: 3px;
  }
  .ct-stat-sep {
    width: 1px;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--color-border-light);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* Hero quote */
  .ct-hero-quote {
    margin: var(--space-6) 0 0;
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }
  .ct-hero-quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .ct-hero-quote cite {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }

  /* Trusted */
  .ct-hero-trusted {
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }
  .ct-trusted-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  .ct-trusted-names {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .ct-trusted-names span {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    padding: 5px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }

  /* Calendly side */
  .ct-hero-cal {
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    min-height: 700px;
  }

  /* ── Social proof strip ── */
  .ct-proof {
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }
  .ct-proof-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-6);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }
  .ct-proof-item { text-align: center; }
  .ct-proof-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .ct-proof-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    display: block;
    margin-top: 3px;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }
  .ct-proof-dot {
    width: 3px;
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-border);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── Process ── */
  .ct-process {
    background: #fff;
    padding: clamp(72px, 9vw, 112px) var(--space-6);
  }
  .ct-process-inner {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .ct-process-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ct-process-card {
    background: #fff;
    padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-6);
  }
  .ct-process-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--color-primary);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .ct-process-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
  }
  .ct-process-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── After the demo ── */
  .ct-after {
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    padding: clamp(72px, 9vw, 112px) var(--space-6);
  }
  .ct-after-inner {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .ct-after-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }
  .ct-after-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    transition: border-color 0.25s ease;
  }
  .ct-after-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border);
  }
  .ct-after-card--accent {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--color-primary);
  }
  .ct-after-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    display: block;
  }
  .ct-after-badge--accent {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  .ct-after-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
  }
  .ct-after-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Migration ── */
  .ct-migrate {
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    padding: clamp(72px, 9vw, 112px) var(--space-6);
  }
  .ct-migrate-inner {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .ct-migrate-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-8);
    max-width: 440px;
  }
  .ct-migrate-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .ct-migrate-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .ct-migrate-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
